                    The Secretary of State to the
                        Ambassador in the United Kingdom (
                        Winant
                    )A parallel instruction was sent to
                            Harriman at the same hour as
                        telegram No. 1526 (file No. 740.0011 E.
                        W./7–545). Winant and
                            Harriman submitted the contents
